# this file describes magic powers available to magical
# order of Necromancy, mostly concerned with the art of
# raising dead souls.
#
# the format for spirits is:
#	name level cost
# and for spells:
#	name level cost duration
#
# where `level' is the magical skill level at which you get the power,
# and `cost' is the cost in spell points to use the power.  `duration'
# tells how long a spell will last.
#
EXEC:CMORTALITY:2
#
summon_ghost_ship 40 1
summon_skeleton 50 1
summon_wraith 80 2
summon_zombie 90 3
summon_poltergeist 120 3
summon_mummy 160 3
summon_ghost 500 5
summon_lacedon 1400 7
summon_lich 2000 14
summon_vampire 2800 15
#
vampire_army 200 2 10
hide_army 200 1 2
hide_sector 250 2 8
mag_bonus 300 1 2
fly_army 400 2 2
water_walk 500 2 2
